// installing PHP in the system

Install xammp (Cross platform Apache MySql and PHP ) server.
Start the MySQL and apache server in it.
Go to C -> xammp -> htdocs -> Make your separate folder -> keep your files here. 




// installing python :-
Download anaconda from the follwing URL :- 
https://www.continuum.io/downloads 
Avaialable for windows/Ubuntu/Mac

It contains python with jupyter Notebook.
After installation,start jupyter notebook. and once the kernel started: access it on (http://localhost:8888/tree)

